title: Lovelyz' Jeong Ye In injures ankle days before comeback + may be unable to promote | allkpop.com

Remember Me Lovelyz' Jeong Ye In injures ankle days before comeback + may be unable to promote By jennywill 2 minutes ago 358 20 0 0 Google+ Lovelyz ' Jeong Ye In has hurt her ankle. Her label said, " She hurt her ankle while practicing for her comeback. Since there isn't that much time left until their comeback, she's currently resting and we're seeing how the ankle heals. " The label added, " We're going to have to see how she heals to decide if she will be able to participate in the comeback promotions. " Hopefully she heals soon!
